p: The title compound was obtained in 59% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.91 (s, 3H), 4.66 (s, 2H), 6.62 (d, J = 7.2 Hz, 1H), 7.16 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.38 (t, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.51 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 7.64 (t, J = 7.5 Hz, 1H), 7.73 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.93 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.98–8.03 (m, 3H), 8.26 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H), 8.94 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H).
